  "description": "Construction of an additional floor to create 1 no. residential unit (associated Listed Building Consent ref: 2024/2241).",
  "subdivision_of_building": "The building is split between RyansN16 public house - on the ground, basement and part 1st floor plans - a studio flat on part 1st floor and a two bed flat on 2nd floor. The new application affects the roof of the building where a new 3rd floor is proposed and minor changes to the entrance of the 2nd floor flat only.",
  "actual_completion_date": null,
  "lpa_app_no": "2024/2240",
  "decision": "Refused",
  "application_type_full": "Full planning & listed building consent",
  "last_updated_by": "Planning Portal ingest",
